title: Introduction
text:
Welcome!
My name is Chiraag Potharaju and I am currently a graduate student enrolled at Virginia Tech taking CS 5804: Introduction to Machine Learning I.

The purpose of this blog is to go in depth about 3 separate topics related to Machine Learning. Throughout the 3 posts in this blog, there will be detailed descriptions, code, and graphs and other diagrams to show various visualizations of these topics.
If there are any questions or issues regarding the content in these posts, feel free to contact me at chiraagp20@vt.edu.
